          "explanation": "Before marriage Repair of vaginal agenesis (seen in testicular feminizaton syndrome and Rokitansky-Kuster Hauser syndrome) is done by vaginoplasty. Vaginoplasty should only be performed when the girl is just married or about to be married. Techniques : 1. Frank dilatation (Non surgical method). 2. Construction of aificial vagina by Mc lndoe operation. 3. Williams vaginoplasty - creates a pouch out of labia majora dissection."
