          "id": "medmcqa-c764a4c5-9b9b-4f9c-9ba8-94abca2a2808",
          "text": "Causes of dysfunctional uterine bleeding can be:a) Uterine polypb) Fibroidc) Granulosa cell tumourd) Irregular ripening of endometriume) Irregular shedding of endometrium",
