          "explanation": "ANSWER: (D) 420REF: This is a question of simple mathematical calculationAverage reproductive life is 35 years from puberty to menopause << There are 12 menstrual cycles every yearOne secondary oocyte is produced in each cycleSo the total number of secondary oocytes produced in female will beSec Oocyte = 35 x 12 x 1= 420",
