          "correctOptionId": "opt-3",
          "explanation": "<p> The basic cause of placenta accreta is decidual deficiency. Associated conditions include implantation in the lower uterine segment over a previous cesarean section scar or any other uterine incision,or after uterine curettage. Reference: Mudaliar and Menon&;s clinical obstetrics,12th edition, page no;330. <\\p>",
