          "text": "A hemodynamically stable nulliparous patient with ectopic pregnancy has adnexal mass of 2.5 x 3 cms and beta hCG titer of 1500 mIU/ml. There is no foetal cardiac activity. Which of the following modality of treatment is suitable for her?",
