          "correctOptionId": "opt-1",
          "explanation": "Danazol is a synthetic testosterone which binds to progesterone and androgen receptors Danazol is used for benign breast diseases and is good for fibrocystic disease. Cyclical mastalgia due to increase engorgement (estrogenic ) will also be relieved with danazol. Almost 70% patients with cyclical mastalgia will repo relief.",
